TIVE PERKS in these areas: There is 100% allowance to work from home Health and medical insurance subscription Team bonding events, several times per year Continuous growth with bi-annual appraisals for consistent self-improvement and goal setting Dynamic environment with regional exposure in an ever-evolving global industry Fun and lively work culture "
